Provenance / attribution (IMPORTANT)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a clean-room-style reimplementation, in C, of the RISC OS Territory
subsystem (the TerritoryManager and TerritoryModule components).  It reproduces
the published Territory SWI ABI.

It is a DERIVATIVE WORK: the per-territory locale data (collation weights,
case/property tables, month and day names, currency symbols, calendar and
time-zone information for the 21 territories) was transcribed from, and the
SWI/entry interfaces follow, the original RISC OS Territory module:

